&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product and Risk to ensure market structures meet both business needs and regulatory standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build standardized templates and rulebooks to streamline how new markets are launched and maintained.&lt;/li&gt;
