&lt;li&gt;Work closely with compliance to incorporate rule changes, disclosure requirements, and governance standards into contracts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay ahead of regulatory developments affecting event contracts and derivatives markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Legal Partnering&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
