&lt;li&gt;Translate complex regulatory and legal concepts into clear, actionable guidance for non-legal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a business-minded partner during negotiations, balancing legal precision with market growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
