&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Roadmap&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are building a novel asset class while scaling up a marketplace for people to trade it (the exchange). As with all meaningful inventions, mass adoption requires value prop refining, education, and trust building. Scaling a new asset class requires both creativity (art) and hardcore discipline (science). We are building our growth team, a cross-functional team of artists and scientists to tackle the uncharted territory of scaling events trading.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As one of the first dedicated performance marketers on the team, you&#39;ll help shape and structure our paid growth strategy by refinding and iterating our value props and messaging in. We are an incredibly content-rich platform: we have over 500 markets and a market for any trending topic out there (Sam Altman leaving OpenAI, Fed cutting rates, Oscars, Biden Approbal, etc.). We are looking to build a dynamic growth machine that capitalizes on trends and viral markets on a weekly basis.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your responsibilities will include:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, iterate, run, and maintain all paid growth efforts, including FB/Instagram, Twitter, and Tiktok&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run our AdWords bidding strategy (with a goal to improve our SEO)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish disciplined end-to-end tracking for our funnel based on different channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve customer attribution and refine our understanding of customer segments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test and iterate on our messaging and value props&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Efficiently scale and manage our paid spend budget (5 to 7 figures)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop creatives and visuals in collaboration with design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create market-specific campaigns targeted at the right audiences (economics, Oscars, tech, AI, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI to develop personalized campaigns (why not)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be bold, make big bets, and have fun.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A scientist at heart who is maniacally disciplined and obsessive about experimenting. A big plus if you&#39;re also creative and have crazy ideas. You&#39;ll thrive in this role if you deeply care about what you produce, you want ownership and freedom (we&#39;re low on process and BS politics), know how to be scrappy and finesse your way around the world, and thrive in a (ridiculously) fast-paced environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
